snippet.title: Kinnikuman Muscle Grand Prix 2 Tokumori Commercial
snippet.description:
Japanese commercial for Kinnikuman Muscle Grand Prix 2 Tokumori (Special Edition). PS2.

This game is a must for any Kinnikuman fan, and for those who enjoy fighting games should definitely give it a try.
